---
// src/components/sections/Mistakes.astro
---
<section class="py-24 px-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
  <div class="text-center mb-16">
    <span class="text-indigo-600 text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-4 block">Avoid These</span>
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-800">Common Mistakes and How to Fix Them</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="space-y-6">
    {[
      { num: "01", title: "Treating Your Journal Like a To-Do List", desc: "Recording tasks is useful, but if that's all you do, you're missing most of what journaling is designed for...", fix: "End every practical entry with 'How I feel about all of this is...'" },
      { num: "02", title: "Writing What You Think You Should Feel", desc: "Journaling for an imagined audience kills the authenticity that makes it work...", fix: "Start with 'What I'm not saying in this journal is...'" }
    ].map(m => (
      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-[32px] border border-slate-100 shadow-sm flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-8">
        <span class="bg-rose-50 text-rose-500 font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-lg text-xs">{m.num}</span>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-3">{m.title}</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">{m.desc}</p>
          <div class="bg-emerald-50/50 text-emerald-600 text-xs font-medium px-4 py-2 rounded-full inline-flex items-center gap-2 border border-emerald-100">
             <span>🔑 Fix:</span> {m.fix}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    ))}
  </div>
</section>